snippet.title: MapleStory 2 Official Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Join the Head Start: http://maplestory2.nexon.net

MapleStory 2 is an all-new MMORPG adventure set in a colorful 3D block universe. Customize your hero, embark on epic quests, build your dream world, and explore a brand new dimension of MapleStory! Adventurers welcome!
